title: #92Noon! 10am Hour 6/3 - Asamoah/Northern Snakehead
description: Vikings rookie linebacker Brian Asamoah calls in to talk about OTAs, all the things he's learned in the NFL so far, & a wide range of other topics.  Plus, PA & Charch deep dive into the world of northern snakehead fish.
